## üéØ Part 2: Component Completion Workflow

### Component Completion Checklist

**ALWAYS** verify before marking component complete:

- [ ] Component implemented (`ComponentName.tsx`)
- [ ] Types defined (`ComponentName.types.ts`)
- [ ] Tests written (`ComponentName.test.tsx`)
- [ ] Tests passing (80%+ coverage)
- [ ] Storybook stories created (`ComponentName.stories.tsx`)
- [ ] JSDoc documentation added
- [ ] Accessibility tested (WCAG AA)
- [ ] Exported through barrel exports
- [ ] No console warnings/errors
- [ ] Code reviewed and linted

### Component Completion Steps

**ALWAYS** follow these steps:

1. Implement component
2. Write tests (TDD approach)
3. Create Storybook stories
4. Add JSDoc documentation
5. Test accessibility
6. Export component
7. Update progress files
8. Mark as complete

